channel.title: Enso II - Recruiting Website Developers
channel.description:
I'm recruiting 2 website developers and one community manager.
What's Enso? Most advanced, unique 667 RuneScape private server ever made. Enso is very promising and will be succesfull RuneScape private server. It's not done for money, it's done for the players. It's a fact the server will become popular since there is no servers in general with the content that Enso has.
Media
[img]http://puu.sh/9CdCd/d7a7e3af8e.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/9BV5O/ba2ecc999d.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/9BWci/768348ee06.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/9CxWW/8fffff4a4f.jpg[/img] [img]http://i43.tinypic.com/2ic1649.png[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/5byeP.jpg[/img] [img]http://i41.tinypic.com/2mq86kn.png[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/5cY3Q.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/5xI4H.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/62ech.png[/img]
That's just some content that I have done, Enso has loads of more that wasn't even 10% of Enso's content.
Best things *Highly advanced combat system. *Unique quest system. Enso has in-built quest guide. *Over 75+ training locations. (to come in this week) *Over 35+ bosses to kill. *Wilderness content. *Full clan wars. *People can F2P pk. *Real 667/667 protocol. Enso is not loading any custom caches. *And so on...
Video of Ape Atoll dungeon, full chinning + rock falling effect. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DKotJ8NH0IA&feature=youtu.be
What you do need to apply? -Website developer You must have skills with the following languages: HTML, PHP, SQL SYSTEMS
-Community manager You must dedicate your time to Enso, you must be very active. Also social skills must be good.
Did one of those optiosn above match you? Contact me by using skype: NexonLTD
